{
  "stem": "11723.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I don't know how this woman got word to my parents that there's no more house above our head, but Uncle Regeur came and he was going to take us back.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And this woman knew Uncle Regeur.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And yet, she said to him, I am personally responsible for these children.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I have to hand them over to the parents.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I can't give them to anybody.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And she knew this man.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I remember that she was hurt in the raid.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She-- a shell hit her, I think the left foot.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She could barely walk, but she came with us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She couldn't wear shoes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She bundled up her feet in rags and she came with us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we had to walk for a while.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think that Uncle Regeur came in an army uniform in order to pass all checkpoints and everything.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he came with an army ambulance.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But in order to get to the army ambulance, I don't know why, we had to walk through the main street of the town.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when we arrived there, they shunted us to the sidewalk.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, in the middle of the street, it was, it was a dusty, real small-town main street where the dust was as thick as fog.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And this is the end of the summer.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I see this ragged bunch of people, hundreds of people, all ages.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There were men and women and children, and some of them carrying bundles, and some of them carrying a little suitcase, and some of them pushing a baby cart, I mean, baby carriage.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they were the Nazis herding them with whips and with the butts of the rifles.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I was standing on the corner of the street.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I hear cheering from all over.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
